N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 263.6 - Director of PEPR and Director of Conciliation

State Regulations

The term
director of PEPR
shall mean the
agent of the board designated as director of private employment practices and
representation. The term
director of conciliation
shall mean
the agent of the board so designated. Notes
